# Path Utils

Use `path_utils` for all paths. Do not hardcode paths or construct them manually.

## Imports

```python
from path_utils import video_cache_path, breakdown_cache_path, breakdown_output_dir, remotion_composite_key, video_public, project_root, prompts_dir, assets_dir, mascot_path, env_path
```

## Key Functions

| Function | Returns |
|----------|---------|
| `video_cache_path(cache_key, config_key, *parts)` | `cache/{config_name}/videos/{cache_key}/parts` — config_key = sanitized config name |
| `breakdown_cache_path(source_hash)` | `cache/_breakdown/{hash}/breakdown.json` (shared across configs) |
| `breakdown_output_dir(source_hash, config_hash)` | `cache/{config_hash}/breakdowns/{hash}/` (videos.md, upload_state.json) |
| `remotion_composite_key(config_hash, cache_key)` | `{config_hash}_{cache_key}` for public/shortgen/ and manifest.cacheKey |
| `video_public()` | `public/` — Remotion static assets |
| `project_root()` | Project root |
| `prompts_dir()` | `generation/prompts/` |
| `assets_dir()` | `generation/assets/` |
| `mascot_path()` | Default mascot canvas |
| `env_path()` | Project .env |

## Rules

1. Cache assets live under `video_cache_path(cache_key, config_hash, ...)` — e.g. `video_cache_path(cache_key, config_hash, "chunks.json")`.
2. Remotion output goes under `video_public() / "shortgen" / remotion_composite_key(config_hash, cache_key)` — manifests, images, voice.
3. Scripts run from project root (e.g. `python generation/scripts/pipeline/run_pipeline.py`); path_utils resolves relative to project root.
